Featured agents (use these exact 4):

Smart Scheduler Agent
Auto-suggest schedules, fill open shifts, warn about conflicts, caregiver availability.

EVV & Timesheet Validator
Flags missing clock-in/out, GPS mismatch, overtime risks, incomplete notes.

Billing & Invoice Builder
Generates invoices from approved shifts, flags missing mileage/expenses, tracks unpaid.

Compliance & Documentation Checker
Detects missing forms (TB, background check, I-9), expiring docs, required signatures.

Only a Few Sections (Most Important)

Do NOT include dozens of sections. Include only these 3 sections below, each with a small heading + short description + a grid of cards.

Section A: “Scheduling & Staffing”

3 cards:

Shift Fill Assistant (finds best caregiver for an open shift)

Conflict Detector (overlaps, travel-time issues, max-hours)

Client Preference Matcher (language, gender preference, skills, distance)

Section B: “Care Delivery & Notes”

3 cards:

Care Note Summarizer (turns daily notes into a clean summary)

Incident Report Drafter (guided incident form + suggested wording)

Family Update Composer (professional update message based on notes)

Section C: “Recruiting & Onboarding”

3 cards:

Applicant Screener (scores candidates, flags missing info)

Onboarding Checklist Agent (steps + documents + reminders)

Training Reminder Agent (CPR renewal, annual training due dates)

