UX Requirements

Desktop: 3–4 column grid; Mobile: 1 column

Smooth hover effects: lift card slightly + subtle border highlight

Empty state: “No agents found. Try ‘billing’ or ‘EVV’.”

Accessibility: buttons have labels, modal focus trap, keyboard close (Esc)

Visual Style Guidance

Background: very light neutral

Cards: white with subtle gradient header bar (small)

Use icons relevant to each agent:

Calendar, Clock, FileText, ShieldCheck, Users, MessageSquare, AlertTriangle, Briefcase, CheckCircle

Keep it “enterprise-clean” and not playful.